{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"6b5dc1959c","title":"岂有此理的“修改宪法要点”","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"31fe202a49","index":0,"year":1957,"month":8,"day":21,"articleId":"6b5dc1959c"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"06bbf56893","name":"新华社"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"f990d5c8da","type":"title","text":"岂有此理的“修改宪法要点”","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6b5dc1959c"},{"id":"f063f17da6","type":"authors","text":"新华社","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6b5dc1959c"},{"id":"ed6147a3bf","type":"paragraph","text":"据新华社南昌18日电： 江西省公路运输厅的资产阶级右派分子、工程师黄振藩已经被揭露出来。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6b5dc1959c"},{"id":"219de7549a","type":"paragraph","text":"黄振藩利用共产党整风的机会，写了一份目的在取消共产党的领导、取消人民民主专政、取消民主集中制的“修改宪法要点”。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6b5dc1959c"},{"id":"c1e61d0303","type":"paragraph","text":"在“修改宪法要点”里，这个右派分子提出要在全国和地方都成立“先进人民代表大会”。在“全国先进人民代表大会”成立以后，现在的全国人民代表大会、全国政协、中国共产党及其他民主党派“均自动宣布解散”，“此后全国任何人不得另组织政治党派”。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6b5dc1959c"},{"id":"68ce0a53de","type":"paragraph","text":" ——原载《人民日报》1957年8月21日。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6b5dc1959c"}],"page":{"id":"04cb7814ff","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6b5dc1959c","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}